one. We had an argument, i said shit, she said shit, i said i'd leave if i didn't get the first plat tear, she said fine whatever...then told mork. Mork asks me if i said this, i said i don't recall everything i said, but yes i said something to the effect, but what does it matter.<br>
<br>
To me this is a personal conversation between two friends, this was not brought up in guild, i didn't threaten the officers or anyone else in any way and i don't know if i woulda or not. Mork removed the though. Only reason IV kills dozekar is because of me, only reason IV is in ssrae is because of me, only reason on a lot of mobs, and i believe most of you agree, is because of me.<br>
<br>
No it is not because i can do it alone, it's because i led and recruited and showed us how to do it. I am sorry that i have to split from IV this way, i'm sorry that mork has the power to guild remove me without consulting any other officer (which no other officer was involved fyi). I quit leading raids for several reasons, i plan to start leading them again, hope some of you care to join.<br>
<br>
I will encourage any and all supporters to bring this up with officers. i would have posted in inner sanctum but my access has been removed.<br>
<br>
I do not intend to return to IV, i am not pleased with this in the slightest, i put a lot of work into this guild and this was a slap in the face to say the least. I am sure i will be bashed for my comments, but fact is, i was removed for a private comment (on the phone) to a friend of 10 years.<br>
<br>
Goodbye and good luck<br>
<br>
Jaharad Van Pelt<br>
